"<p><span class=\"block-image image-wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://ka-perseus-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7b84b185749061b46f01a5c1b9ed612d586a7cce.jpg\" /><span class=\"image-caption\">William Holman Hunt, <em>Our English Coasts</em> (<em>Strayed Sheep</em>), 1852, oil on canvas, 43.2 x 58.4 cm (London, Tate Britain)</span></span></p>\n"
