"\" src=\"https://ka-perseus-images.s3.amazonaws.com/c2fdbf418a1fd07480eddf96b68b8206e83d6ea3.jpg\" /><span class=\"image-caption\">Right: Sants Maria del Carmine, Florence; right:&nbsp;Brancacci Chapel, with frescoes by Masaccio and Masolino, Santa Maria del Carmine,<br />\n"
