"<p><span class=\"image-wrapper inline-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://ka-perseus-images.s3.amazonaws.com/bb33a5fa31d530967d4d94b9128211539a1f0915.png\" /><span class=\"image-caption\">Caryle and Maurice (detail) Ford Madox Brown, <em>Work</em>, 1852-65, oil on canvas, 137 x 197.3 cm (Manchester City Art Galleries)</span></span><br />\n"
