"&nbsp;</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><span class=\"block-image image-wrapper\"><img alt=\"Frank Lloyd Wright, Fallingwater, detail with tree (Edgar J. Kaufmann House), 1937 (photo: Daderot, CC0 1.0) http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Fallingwater_detail_-_DSC05656.JPG\" src=\"https://ka-perseus-images.s3.amazonaws.com/3d5192a7201493738e84e2bb82d6e960f317ca2a.jpg\" /><span class=\"image-caption\">Frank Lloyd Wright, Fallingwater, detail with tree (Edgar J.&nbsp;Kaufmann House), 1937 (photo: <a href=\"http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Fallingwater_detail_-_DSC05656.JPG\">Daderot</a>, CC0 1.0)&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n"
