"<p>Jean-Paul Sartre,&nbsp;<em>Anti-Semite and Jew</em>, translated by George J. Becker (New York:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Schocken Books, 1948).</p>\n"
