"<p><span class=\"image-wrapper inline-image\"><img alt=\"Shiva as Lord of the Dance (Nataraja), c. 11th century, Copper alloy, Chola period, 68.3 x 56.5 cm (The Metropolitan Museum of Art) \" src=\"https://ka-perseus-images.s3.amazonaws.com/92f80ab3534af89c8c6e8fe7c87d3eb3dcdbcc61.jpg\" /><span class=\"image-caption\"><em>Shiva as Lord of the Dance (Nataraja)</em>, c. 11th century, Copper alloy, Chola period, 68.3 x 56.5 cm (The Metropolitan Museum of Art) </span></span></p>\n"
